overview.en: AMIGO uses blockchain technology to ensure the credibility of content, uses an economic incentive system to accelerate the generation and circulation of high-quality content, and uses a reputation system to contribute pricing and equity returns to the content production field.
overview.zh: AMIGO 使用区块链技术保证内容的可信性，使用经济激励体系加速高质量内容的产生和流通，使用信誉系统为内容生产领域进行贡献定价和权益回报。
